00:11:06.966 --> 00:11:08.000
Male Speaker: The Department
of Defense Medal for

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:10.569
Distinguished Public Service
is presented to

00:11:10.569 --> 00:11:12.805
President Barack Obama.

00:11:12.805 --> 00:11:15.441
President Barack Obama
distinguished himself as the

00:11:15.441 --> 00:11:18.077
Commander-In-Chief of the
finest fighting force the

00:11:18.077 --> 00:11:22.048
world has every known from
January 20, 2009 to

00:11:22.048 --> 00:11:24.784
January 20, 2017.

00:11:24.784 --> 00:11:28.020
President Obama kept our
nation safe, led a strategic

00:11:28.020 --> 00:11:31.157
transition in our defense
strategy, strengthened our

00:11:31.157 --> 00:11:34.393
alliances and pursued new
partnerships, and laid the

00:11:34.393 --> 00:11:36.729
foundation for a force
of the future that will

00:11:36.729 --> 00:11:39.498
continue to win
our nation's wars.

00:11:39.498 --> 00:11:42.134
President Obama countered
decisively the immediate

00:11:42.134 --> 00:11:45.504
threat to our national
security -- terrorism.

00:11:45.504 --> 00:11:48.574
He directed the operation
to kill Osama Bin Laden,

00:11:48.574 --> 00:11:51.243
decimated Al Qaeda's
terrorist network, put the

00:11:51.243 --> 00:11:53.946
Islamic state of Iraq and
Levant on a path to a

00:11:53.946 --> 00:11:56.615
lasting defeat, and
developed counterterrorism

00:11:56.615 --> 00:11:59.919
platforms from South
Asia to North Africa.

00:11:59.919 --> 00:12:03.522
He did so relentlessly,
effectively, with increased

00:12:03.522 --> 00:12:07.159
transparency, and in strict
accordance with our values.

00:12:07.159 --> 00:12:10.329
Simultaneously, President
Obama achieved verifiable

00:12:10.329 --> 00:12:13.365
nuclear disarmament to
Iran, the gravest threat to

00:12:13.365 --> 00:12:15.835
security in the Middle East.

00:12:15.835 --> 00:12:18.137
And while countering
proliferation abroad, he

00:12:18.137 --> 00:12:20.973
directed recapitalization
of our vitally important

00:12:20.973 --> 00:12:23.576
nuclear deterrent
here at home.

00:12:23.576 --> 00:12:25.411
As he successfully
neutralized immediate

00:12:25.411 --> 00:12:28.314
threats to our security,
President Obama also

00:12:28.314 --> 00:12:31.484
directed a transition
in our defense strategy.

00:12:31.484 --> 00:12:34.487
He implemented a rigorous
intellectual policy and

00:12:34.487 --> 00:12:37.556
legal framework to guide the
most solemn decision that a

00:12:37.556 --> 00:12:41.360
commander-in-chief makes --
to deploy and employ our men

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:43.762
and women in uniform.

00:12:43.762 --> 00:12:46.265
He supported strategic
investments to perpetuate

00:12:46.265 --> 00:12:50.035
our military edge in the
air, at sea, with missile

00:12:50.035 --> 00:12:53.739
defenses, and in space and
cyber domains including by

00:12:53.739 --> 00:12:56.775
establishing the United
States Cyber Command.

00:12:56.775 --> 00:12:59.545
In so doing, he led the
transformation of the United

00:12:59.545 --> 00:13:02.915
States military from over a
decade of counterinsurgency

00:13:02.915 --> 00:13:05.384
into a full spectrum
fighting force.

00:13:05.384 --> 00:13:08.220
And critically, he directed
the United States rebalance

00:13:08.220 --> 00:13:11.223
to the Asia-Pacific, the
most consequential region

00:13:11.223 --> 00:13:13.092
for America's future.

00:13:13.092 --> 00:13:15.628
President Obama also
recognized that security in

00:13:15.628 --> 00:13:17.296
the world cannot be
America's

00:13:17.296 --> 00:13:19.498
responsibility alone.

00:13:19.498 --> 00:13:21.734
He strengthened our
alliances and pursued

00:13:21.734 --> 00:13:23.302
new partnerships.

00:13:23.302 --> 00:13:25.704
In Europe, he led the
adaptation of NATO to

00:13:25.704 --> 00:13:29.074
continue its commitment to
a stable Afghanistan and to

00:13:29.074 --> 00:13:32.811
actively counter threats to
Europe's east and south.

00:13:32.811 --> 00:13:34.914
In particular, President
Obama directed the

00:13:34.914 --> 00:13:38.017
bolstering of our Allied
Military Presence in Europe

00:13:38.017 --> 00:13:40.119
and reestablishing of
deterrents against

00:13:40.119 --> 00:13:41.687
Russian aggression.

00:13:41.687 --> 00:13:44.757
In Asia, he modernized our
alliances with Japan and

00:13:44.757 --> 00:13:47.826
Korea strengthening the
cornerstone of security in

00:13:47.826 --> 00:13:51.463
East Asia, and deterring
threats from North Korea.

00:13:51.463 --> 00:13:53.332
In the Middle East, he
strengthened Israel's

00:13:53.332 --> 00:13:56.135
qualitative military
edge including with an

00:13:56.135 --> 00:13:59.238
unprecedented package of
foreign military funding.

00:13:59.238 --> 00:14:01.807
But in an ever-changing
world, President Obama

00:14:01.807 --> 00:14:05.744
recognized that America's
relationships must also change.

00:14:05.744 --> 00:14:09.615
He directed the advancement
of new strategic (inaudible)

00:14:09.615 --> 00:14:11.684
including the unprecedented
deepening of the

00:14:11.684 --> 00:14:16.088
strategically consequential
United States-India partnership.

00:14:16.088 --> 00:14:18.791
In all of this, President
Obama recognized that the

00:14:18.791 --> 00:14:21.493
source of America's greatest
strength, including its

00:14:21.493 --> 00:14:24.129
military strength,
is its people.

00:14:24.129 --> 00:14:26.298
To ensure that the United
States military stays the

00:14:26.298 --> 00:14:29.835
best, he understood that we
must continue to attract,

00:14:29.835 --> 00:14:33.239
recruit, retain, develop,
and transition the best

00:14:33.239 --> 00:14:35.975
talent that our
nation has to offer.

00:14:35.975 --> 00:14:38.611
His repealing of the Don't
Ask, Don't Tell Policy, and

00:14:38.611 --> 00:14:41.513
the support for opening all
military occupations and

00:14:41.513 --> 00:14:44.683
positions to women
will help ensure that.

00:14:44.683 --> 00:14:47.753
He also championed advanced
research and an innovative

00:14:47.753 --> 00:14:50.789
program to care for our
nation's wounded warriors

00:14:50.789 --> 00:14:53.592
and their families and led
efforts to help veterans

00:14:53.592 --> 00:14:56.161
make the transition
to civilian life.

00:14:56.161 --> 00:14:58.230
These and many other
distinctive accomplishments

00:14:58.230 --> 00:15:01.500
of President Obama reflect
great credit upon himself,

00:15:01.500 --> 00:15:04.003
the Department of Defense,
and the United

00:15:04.003 --> 00:15:05.504
States of America.

00:15:05.504 --> 00:15:10.209
(applause)

